I am the supervisor

297
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:44,840
of this competition.

298
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:45,770
I have to sign off

299
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,080
on the final results.

300
00:10:47,790 --> 00:10:48,390
Mr. Wang,

301
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,030
do you think that after I exposed

302
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:51,510
our personal grudge,

303
00:10:51,870 --> 00:10:53,870
you are still qualified to sign off?

304
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:55,800
You have no evidence

305
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:57,210
to prove I cheated,

306
00:10:57,570 --> 00:10:58,840
but I have the ability to prove

307
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,480
that I am qualified

308
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,550
to be on that stage.

309
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:03,440
From the moment you questioned me,

310
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,800
you had already lost.

311
00:11:06,550 --> 00:11:07,550
It's not over yet.

312
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:10,670
Neither of us knows who the winner is.

313
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:13,270
Xia Ziyu didn't admit defeat either,

314
00:11:13,270 --> 00:11:14,670
so she became a fugitive.

315
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:16,350
You are just like her—

316
00:11:16,510 --> 00:11:17,570
just as shameless.

317
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,510
You assume

318
00:11:18,510 --> 00:11:19,970
everyone is just like you.

319
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:21,270
But sorry,

320
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,550
I, Xia Xiaolan,

321
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,080
rely on my own abilities

322
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,340
to get where I am today.

323
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:26,910
Your crooked ways

324
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:28,240
can't stop me.

325
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,480
Because of you, Jianhua

326
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,810
can't even go to school.

327
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:33,270
Why should you
have a better life than him?

328
00:11:33,270 --> 00:11:35,130
I won't let you get away with this.

329
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,600
Dropping the highest

330
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,870
and the lowest score...

331
00:11:37,870 --> 00:11:38,240
Okay.

332
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,360
Our contestant No.16's

333
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,480
final score is

334
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:42,240
97.3 points.

335
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,250
Xiaolan,

336
00:11:47,550 --> 00:11:48,270
go and accept

337
00:11:48,270 --> 00:11:49,930
the honor that belongs to you.

338
00:11:50,380 --> 00:11:50,840
Okay.

339
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:57,770
Mr. Wang,

340
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,600
you can no longer change

341
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,030
the result of the competition.

342
00:12:01,030 --> 00:12:01,600
If you still have

343
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,930
a shred of rationality,

344
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:04,560
save yourself some dignity.

345
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:08,640
[The Finals Of The First National College English Competition Of The Chengrong Cup]

346
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:05,440
And now,

347
00:12:05,750 --> 00:12:07,030
the winner of
the First National College Student

348
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,750
English Competition Finals

349
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,910
has been decided.

350
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:10,760
She is

351
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:12,080
contestant No.12

352
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,080
from Huaqing University,

353
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,030
Xia Xiaolan.

354
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:16,230
See? I told you our Xiaolan

355
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:18,180
would definitely be first place.

356
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,080
Who are you?

357
00:12:53,550 --> 00:12:54,880
Who do you think you are?

358
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,060
Let me tell you,

359
00:12:56,550 --> 00:12:57,750
without my sign-off,

360
00:12:57,870 --> 00:12:59,670
Xia Xiaolan is nothing.

361
00:12:59,790 --> 00:13:01,120
What an abuse of power.

362
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:03,600
How about

363
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,780
I sign it off, then?

364
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:05,960
Minister Tang,

365
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,890
why are you here?

366
00:13:06,910 --> 00:13:09,150
The Ministry sent you
to supervise the competition,

367
00:13:09,150 --> 00:13:10,720
not to throw your weight around

368
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:12,320
and settle personal grudges.

369
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,200
If Zhan hadn't

370
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,120
sent someone in time

371
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,850
to tell me what's going on here,

372
00:13:16,070 --> 00:13:16,670
I'm afraid

373
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,480
this first English competition

374
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:20,200
would have been the last.

375
00:13:20,420 --> 00:13:21,550
Minister Tang, you don't know,

376
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:22,240
this Xia Xiaolan,

377
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:22,870
there's definitely
something wrong with her—

378
00:13:22,870 --> 00:13:23,800
Wang Guangping,

379
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,170
watch yourself.

380
00:13:25,510 --> 00:13:26,840
Have you lost your mind?

381
00:13:27,030 --> 00:13:27,480
Yes,

382
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,930
I've gone crazy.

383
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,450
I went crazy 4 years ago.

384
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:32,110
They ruined my son's life,

385
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,600
so I'm going to ruin theirs!

386
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,000
You...

387
00:13:34,510 --> 00:13:37,200
No one can ruin anyone else's life.

388
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:40,080
We all walk our own paths.

389
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:41,320
Are you the one questioning

390
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,050
our Xiaolan?

391
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,000
Who do you think you are?

392
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,670
I'm telling you,

393
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:50,210
as a village girl, it's not easy

394
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:51,600
that Xiaolan made it here

395
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,550
step by step.

396
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,270
She suffered

397
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:55,320
and toiled.

398
00:13:55,910 --> 00:13:57,390
Yet she has to be sabotaged
by someone like you—

399
00:13:57,390 --> 00:13:58,450
a malicious

400
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:00,030
and narrow-minded man

401
00:14:00,030 --> 00:14:01,510
making things difficult for her.

402
00:14:01,510 --> 00:14:02,970
But she never complained!

403
00:14:03,290 --> 00:14:04,840
You failed to raise your own child well,

404
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,840
so you take it out on a young girl.

405
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:09,170
Reflect on your own issues.

406
00:14:09,200 --> 00:14:10,270
Ma'am, Ma'am.

407
00:14:10,290 --> 00:14:11,290
Please calm down.

408
00:14:12,090 --> 00:14:12,670
We will make sure

409
00:14:12,670 --> 00:14:14,050
we will be fair towards Ms. Xia

410
00:14:14,050 --> 00:14:14,980
for this matter.

411
00:14:15,270 --> 00:14:16,270
We all saw Xiaolan's performance

412
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:17,390
today.

413
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:19,320
You don't need to be fair to her.

414
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,580
She earned it herself.

415
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:26,720
Let's give another round of applause

416
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,510
to our second

417
00:14:27,510 --> 00:14:29,200
and third-place winners.

418
00:14:30,150 --> 00:14:32,080
Students, you may leave the stage.

419
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,120
Now we have arrived at

420
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,960
the most exciting moment of the day.

421
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:35,960
Let's once again

422
00:14:36,170 --> 00:14:38,170
welcome today's champion,

423
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:40,790
Xia Xiaolan from Huaqing University.

424
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,270
Let's welcome

425
00:14:43,270 --> 00:14:44,600
Professor Xu Guozhang

426
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:46,120
and Mr. Du Zhaohui

427
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:47,030
from Chengrong Group

428
00:14:47,030 --> 00:14:48,830
to present the award to Xiaolan.

429
00:14:57,580 --> 00:14:59,580
[Certificate of Honor]

430
00:14:58,090 --> 00:14:59,150
Congratulations.

431
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,790
Were you not afraid

432
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:03,960
of offending me
with what you said just now?

433
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:04,390
No.

434
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:06,510
I trust you are fair.

435
00:15:07,190 --> 00:15:07,870
Xiaolan,

436
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,610
you really are one of a kind.

437
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:10,360
Thank you.

438
00:15:13,670 --> 00:15:14,400
Pretty girl,

439
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:15,670
you've got a bright future.

440
00:15:15,670 --> 00:15:16,270
Thank you.

441
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,240
I believe at this moment

442
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,480
Xiaolan has a lot

443
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,750
she wants to share with us.

444
00:15:22,750 --> 00:15:23,240
Please.

445
00:15:26,390 --> 00:15:27,510
First of all,

446
00:15:27,510 --> 00:15:29,480
I am very happy to receive this award.

447
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:30,960
I want to thank my university,

448
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:32,750
Huaqing University, for nurturing me.

449
00:15:32,750 --> 00:15:33,600
I want to thank my teachers

450
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:35,080
for their dedicated guidance.

451
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,440
And I want to thank our country

452
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,910
for its growing prosperity,

453
00:15:37,910 --> 00:15:38,830
which gave me the opportunity

454
00:15:38,830 --> 00:15:39,990
to learn English.

455
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,750
I also thank the judges here

456
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:43,960
who always strive for fairness,

457
00:15:44,210 --> 00:15:45,240
for giving me a chance

458
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:46,720
to prove myself.

459
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:47,720
Finally,

460
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,420
I want to thank my enemies.

461
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:50,600
It is because of them

462
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:52,200
that I never let my guard down

463
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:54,480
and keep moving forward.

464
00:15:54,790 --> 00:15:55,390
Thank you.

465
00:15:58,820 --> 00:15:59,240
Very well.

466
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:00,720
Thank you, Xiaolan,
for that wonderful speech.

467
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:01,480
And here,

468
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:02,550
I would also like to thank

469
00:16:02,550 --> 00:16:04,240
all the teachers and students present

470
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:06,000
for supporting the Chengrong Cup.

471
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:06,600
I declare

472
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:09,030
the Finals Of The First National College English Competition

473
00:16:09,030 --> 00:16:10,160
Of The Chengrong Cup

474
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:11,780
successfully concluded!

475
00:16:12,910 --> 00:16:13,960
We would also like to invite

476
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:14,790
all students and teachers

477
00:16:14,790 --> 00:16:16,990
to come onto the stage for a group photo.

478
00:16:26,910 --> 00:16:27,630
Please make some space for me.

479
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:28,600
Thank you.

480
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,260
Get ready. Come on.

481
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:31,120
Ms. Xia,

482
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:32,450
congratulations.

483
00:16:32,810 --> 00:16:33,240
Thank you.

484
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:34,170
Okay, get ready.

485
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:36,080
Look here.

486
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,910
3, 2, 1.

487
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:40,460
Okay, one more.

488
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:42,130
Look at me. Here.

489
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:43,840
3, 2, 1.

490
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:44,870
Okay.

491
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:46,270
Perfect.

492
00:16:46,790 --> 00:16:48,990
Thank you for your hard work, everyone.

493
00:16:49,030 --> 00:16:49,600
Xiaolan,

494
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,850
your English is amazing.

495
00:16:50,850 --> 00:16:51,550
How did you practice?

496
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:52,120
Yeah, exactly.

497
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:53,600
We want to learn from you.

498
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:54,320
Let's communicate.

499
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,510
I'm from Huaqing University.

500
00:16:55,510 --> 00:16:56,630
You can send letters to me.

501
00:16:56,630 --> 00:16:57,550
I will receive them.

502
00:16:57,550 --> 00:16:58,960
Okay, we'll write to you often.

503
00:16:58,960 --> 00:16:59,840
Let's keep in touch.

504
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:00,550
Okay. Bye-bye!

505
00:17:00,550 --> 00:17:01,120
-Let's go.
-Bye-bye!

506
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:01,720
Ms. Xia...

507
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:04,800
You...

508
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:05,730
Xiaolan,

509
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,200
congratulations.

510
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:07,720
What are you doing?

511
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:08,750
This is too much.

512
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:09,750
I have to be.

513
00:17:09,930 --> 00:17:11,589
You even gave them your mailing address.

514
00:17:11,589 --> 00:17:13,240
First letters, then mutual encouragement,

515
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:14,790
and then studying together—

516
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:16,589
I know this routine all too well.

517
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:18,900
Do you want some water?

518
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:20,589
Are you thirsty?

519
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,290
I want to talk to her.

520
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:25,200
Her?

521
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:27,270
I think I just saw

522
00:17:27,550 --> 00:17:28,880
Mrs. Guan. Was she here?

523
00:17:29,310 --> 00:17:29,590
Yes.

524
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:30,880
Grandma is here too.

525
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:31,400
They were

526
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,290
defending you against everyone just now too.

527
00:17:33,290 --> 00:17:34,640
Excuse me!

528
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:36,750
My boss,

529
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:38,350
who sponsored this contest,

530
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:39,830
would like to have a chat with you.

531
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:41,000
The one in white.

532
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:43,010
After all, he paid for this.

533
00:17:43,330 --> 00:17:44,550
Please show some respect.

534
00:17:44,550 --> 00:17:45,510
He is the boss.

535
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:46,750
Sure.

536
00:17:50,180 --> 00:17:51,750
Wait here.

537
00:17:53,110 --> 00:17:54,000
Hello, Mr. Du.

538
00:17:54,030 --> 00:17:55,090
What's the matter?

539
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:56,270
Ms. Xia,

540
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:57,240
you are even prettier offstage

541
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:58,200
than on stage.

542
00:17:58,590 --> 00:18:00,320
Why don't we go somewhere quiet

543
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:00,950
for a chat?

544
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:02,600
Thank you.

545
00:18:02,830 --> 00:18:04,030
Let's just talk here.

546
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:05,370
Want a smoke?

547
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:06,510
No, thanks.

548
00:18:06,510 --> 00:18:07,310
I don't smoke.

549
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:08,760
That's good.

550
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:13,810
Are you really Xia Dajun's daughter?

551
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:18,110
Go, Young Master!

552
00:18:18,110 --> 00:18:18,640
Hurry up.

553
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:19,640
Come on, go!

554
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,200
-Kun!
-Kun, Kun!

555
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:31,270
You're hurt.

556
00:18:31,270 --> 00:18:31,720
Dajun.

557
00:18:32,240 --> 00:18:33,350
Protect Young Master.

558
00:18:33,350 --> 00:18:34,270
Protect Young Master.

559
00:18:34,270 --> 00:18:34,720
Okay.

560
00:18:35,240 --> 00:18:36,300
Get him out of here!

561
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:37,350
Hurry, Kun!

562
00:18:37,350 --> 00:18:37,790
Go!

563
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:45,960
Get in the car!

564
00:18:46,720 --> 00:18:47,120
Hurry!

565
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:47,560
Hurry!

566
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,240
Go!

567
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:07,520
You're awake.

568
00:19:12,510 --> 00:19:13,040
Lie down.

569
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:16,460
You worked for Kun?

570
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:21,160
Kun is gone.

571
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:23,940
Work for me from now on.

572
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:25,960
I don't care

573
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:27,090
where you came from.

574
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,510
Since you saved me,

575
00:19:28,510 --> 00:19:29,640
I'll treat you well.

576
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:31,970
Just rest and heal up first.

577
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:33,900
Do you have any family?

578
00:19:34,510 --> 00:19:36,240
I can help take care of them too.

579
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:37,720
I...

580
00:19:38,830 --> 00:19:40,720
I have a daughter.

581
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:44,400
She's studying at Huaqing University.

582
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:46,440
When he told me,

583
00:19:46,550 --> 00:19:48,040
I thought his brain was damaged.

584
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:48,590
I didn't expect

585
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:50,510
someone like you to actually exist.

586
00:19:50,510 --> 00:19:51,160
Mr. Du.

587
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:52,880
What exactly do you want?

588
00:19:53,350 --> 00:19:54,750
It's about what you want.

589
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:55,850
He saved my life.

590
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:57,460
Just tell me what you want.

591
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:59,300
Whether it's a job in Gangdao,

592
00:19:59,350 --> 00:20:00,480
residency,

593
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:02,830
or even going abroad—
I can help you with them.

594
00:20:02,830 --> 00:20:03,110
Mr. Du—

595
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:03,960
But looking at you,

596
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:05,090
you're so beautiful

597
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,090
and articulate.

598
00:20:06,510 --> 00:20:07,640
Why not go to Gangdao

599
00:20:07,750 --> 00:20:08,720
to join a beauty pageant,

600
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:10,380
become a charity ambassador,

601
00:20:10,510 --> 00:20:12,110
and then become a movie star?

602
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:13,000
It's a glamorous life.

603
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:13,480
No need.

604
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:15,220
Thanks for your offer.

605
00:20:15,350 --> 00:20:17,000
My parents divorced a long time ago.

606
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:17,680
Xia Dajun and I

607
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:18,830
have no contact.

608
00:20:19,350 --> 00:20:20,480
If something happens to him,

609
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:21,830
I'll fulfill my duty to support him,

610
00:20:21,830 --> 00:20:23,750
but I don't care about anything else.

611
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:24,200
Also,

612
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:25,350
I don't need

613
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:26,800
him arranging my future.

614
00:20:26,830 --> 00:20:28,880
And I don't want to
go to Gangdao in the future.

615
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:29,110
Well...

616
00:20:29,110 --> 00:20:30,840
Is there anything else, Mr. Du?

617
00:20:31,510 --> 00:20:32,590
If there's nothing else,

618
00:20:32,590 --> 00:20:33,390
I'll be going.

619
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:34,740
Let's go, Xiaolan.

620
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:36,880
This is my boyfriend,

621
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:37,540
Zhou Cheng.

622
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:43,440
Young Master.

623
00:20:43,510 --> 00:20:44,680
She rejected you.

624
00:20:46,310 --> 00:20:47,200
Xia Dajun

625
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:48,400
can give birth

626
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:49,800
to such a smart daughter?

627
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:51,270
Keep tabs on her news.

628
00:20:51,270 --> 00:20:52,590
She's graduating soon.

629
00:20:52,590 --> 00:20:53,920
I want to see what career

630
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,200
is better than being a star

631
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:55,860
in Gangdao.

632
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:57,550
Sure thing. Leave it to me.

633
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:00,510
My grandma goes to bed early,

634
00:21:00,510 --> 00:21:02,110
so my mom took her home first.

635
00:21:02,350 --> 00:21:02,920
By the way,

636
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:04,350
she said she'll throw you
a proper celebration

637
00:21:04,350 --> 00:21:05,720
this weekend at home.

638
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:07,850
Why didn't you tell me

639
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:10,010
that your mom and grandma were coming?

640
00:21:10,070 --> 00:21:11,830
I wanted to surprise you.

641
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:14,460
But it turned into a shock, didn't it?

642
00:21:14,830 --> 00:21:15,440
Not at all.

643
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:17,200
They think you were very brave.

644
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:18,660
They're very proud of you.

645
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:20,510
Why weren't you angry

646
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:22,640
when that sponsor reached out to me?

647
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:24,360
Why should I be angry?

648
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:31,310
That guy just now

649
00:21:31,310 --> 00:21:32,880
said he's Xia Dajun's boss.

650
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:33,720
He asked if I wanted

651
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:35,270
to use my employee benefits.

652
00:21:35,270 --> 00:21:36,550
He said he'd send me to Gangdao

653
00:21:36,550 --> 00:21:37,640
to be a movie star.

654
00:21:40,890 --> 00:21:41,850
A movie star?

655
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:44,070
You didn't refuse, did you?

656
00:21:45,510 --> 00:21:46,790
Why would I go to Gangdao?

657
00:21:46,790 --> 00:21:47,960
My application for early graduation

658
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,020
has been approved.

659
00:21:49,070 --> 00:21:50,480
I'm going all the way south

660
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:52,140
and build up the special zone!

661
00:21:54,190 --> 00:21:58,010
[Longcheng] [Jingcheng]

662
00:22:02,910 --> 00:22:06,530
[Longcheng Station]

663
00:22:23,350 --> 00:22:24,160
Yong!

664
00:22:25,310 --> 00:22:26,070
Are they almost here?

665
00:22:26,070 --> 00:22:26,930
Any minute now.

666
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:39,840
Over here!

667
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:40,640
Over here!

668
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:41,680
Xiaolan!

669
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:42,680
Bai!

670
00:22:46,350 --> 00:22:47,160
Uncle!

671
00:22:51,030 --> 00:22:51,480
Sorry, sorry.

672
00:22:51,480 --> 00:22:51,880
Hey!

673
00:22:52,350 --> 00:22:53,200
Xiaolan!

674
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:55,480
Let me introduce you.

675
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:56,680
This is my mom, Liu Fen.

676
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,070
Hello, Ma'am.

677
00:22:57,070 --> 00:22:57,440
Hello.

678
00:22:57,440 --> 00:22:57,970
And this

679
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,600
is my boyfriend, Zhou Cheng.

680
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:01,670
Hello, Comrade Bai Zhenzhu.

681
00:23:01,790 --> 00:23:02,590
Hello, hello.

682
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:04,550
I've heard Xiaolan mention you often.

683
00:23:04,550 --> 00:23:05,350
No need to be so formal.

684
00:23:05,350 --> 00:23:06,200
Just call me Sis Bai.

685
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:06,660
Sis Bai.

686
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:08,640
This is my good friend,

687
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:09,030
Kang Wei.

688
00:23:09,030 --> 00:23:09,750
Hello, hello.

689
00:23:09,750 --> 00:23:10,240
Hello.

690
00:23:10,510 --> 00:23:11,350
Since we're all here,

691
00:23:11,350 --> 00:23:13,080
let's take a picture together.

692
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:13,720
Okay.

693
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:14,720
Let's go.

694
00:23:16,030 --> 00:23:16,440
Come on.

695
00:23:16,440 --> 00:23:17,570
I'll take it for you.

696
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:18,940
Come on.

697
00:23:20,550 --> 00:23:21,160
Ready?

698
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:22,240
Stand still.

699
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:25,200
3, 2, 1.

700
00:23:25,350 --> 00:23:26,350
Smile!

701
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:28,200
Good shot!

702
00:23:31,600 --> 00:23:31,970
Wait.

703
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,330
Someone slashed my bag!

704
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:35,960
Who was it?

705
00:23:35,980 --> 00:23:37,510
Who stole my wallet?

706
00:23:37,600 --> 00:23:37,930
Hey!

707
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:38,750
Who was it?

708
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:39,350
Who?

709
00:23:39,350 --> 00:23:39,960
That's enough, Wei.

710
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:41,020
When did it happen?

711
00:23:41,350 --> 00:23:42,680
Was it when we were leaving the station,

712
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:43,480
or on the train?

713
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:44,030
When I got off the train,

714
00:23:44,030 --> 00:23:45,070
it was still there.

715
00:23:45,070 --> 00:23:45,880
Did someone bump into you

716
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:47,160
when you left the train station?

717
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:47,480
Yes.

718
00:23:50,070 --> 00:23:50,590
Sorry, sorry.

719
00:23:50,590 --> 00:23:50,960
Hey.

720
00:23:52,960 --> 00:23:53,640
People in Longcheng

721
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:54,920
are too savage.

722
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:55,720
I just got off the train,

723
00:23:55,720 --> 00:23:56,920
and I get a "welcome gift" like this.

724
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:57,520
Young man,

725
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:58,880
watch your language.

726
00:23:59,030 --> 00:24:00,680
People in Longcheng aren't like that.

727
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:02,030
Those are just a few bad apples.

728
00:24:02,030 --> 00:24:02,880
S-Stop talking.

729
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:04,340
Let's help Wei look for it.

730
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:05,480
-Okay.
-Mrs. Liu.

731
00:24:05,590 --> 00:24:06,320
Don't worry.

732
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:07,610
Leave this to me.

733
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:09,750
Aren't you guys going to Shengcheng?

734
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:11,160
Take Yong's car

735
00:24:11,180 --> 00:24:11,910
and go ahead.

736
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:13,920
Rest assured,

737
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,750
we'll definitely find the wallet for you.

738
00:24:15,750 --> 00:24:16,830
Once we find it,

739
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,780
we'll take the bus to Shengcheng.

740
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:19,880
I don't want people saying

741
00:24:19,880 --> 00:24:21,350
that folks in Longcheng aren't honorable.

742
00:24:21,350 --> 00:24:22,070
Forget it, forget it.

743
00:24:22,070 --> 00:24:23,270
Let's not trouble this young lady.

744
00:24:23,270 --> 00:24:24,550
Okay, we'll do as you say.

745
00:24:24,550 --> 00:24:25,070
Wei,

746
00:24:25,270 --> 00:24:26,350
Bai is my

747
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:27,200
most reliable friend.

748
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:27,920
Trust her.

749
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:29,550
Okay.

750
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:30,780
All right then.

751
00:24:30,890 --> 00:24:31,440
Give that to me.

752
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:32,430
My car is right over there.

753
00:24:32,430 --> 00:24:32,830
Take this suitcase.

754
00:24:32,830 --> 00:24:33,200
Here.

755
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,060
Let me get that.

756
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:34,510
Here.

757
00:24:35,640 --> 00:24:36,070
Then you guys...

758
00:24:36,070 --> 00:24:37,200
Don't worry, Mrs. Liu.

759
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,000
See you later.

760
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:38,640
Go on.

761
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:39,550
Be careful.

762
00:24:39,790 --> 00:24:40,840
See you later.

763
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:45,000
Bai, how are we going to find it?

764
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:45,600
Follow me.

765
00:24:48,740 --> 00:24:49,540
Let's go, Mom.

766
00:24:52,030 --> 00:24:53,830
Let's wait for them a bit longer.

767
00:24:55,550 --> 00:24:56,880
From what Bai said just now,

768
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:58,740
she seems to know who the thief is.

769
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:00,400
It's the thugs

770
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:01,460
around the train station.

771
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:03,200
Bai used to do business here,

772
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,590
so she's dealt with them.

773
00:25:04,590 --> 00:25:05,510
When I came here before,

774
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:06,970
they also gave me trouble.

775
00:25:07,000 --> 00:25:08,200
Bai took care of it all.

776
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:08,930
Don't worry.

777
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:11,110
So the train station has become

778
00:25:11,110 --> 00:25:12,570
their lawless territory?

779
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:13,920
Is there no one to keep them in check?

780
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:15,790
Someone will deal with them
sooner or later.

781
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:16,320
Let's go.

782
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:17,410
Let's go.

783
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:18,970
Let's go.

784
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:21,380
Sis Bai.

785
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:21,920
Sorry I was being rude

786
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:23,000
just now.

787
00:25:23,120 --> 00:25:24,160
Let me introduce myself properly.

788
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:24,890
I'm Kang Wei.

789
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:26,680
I'm Zhou Cheng's childhood friend.

790
00:25:26,680 --> 00:25:27,590
I've heard how

791
00:25:27,590 --> 00:25:28,400
you stuck your neck out

792
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:29,530
for Xiaolan before.

793
00:25:29,530 --> 00:25:30,160
I've heard a lot about you.

794
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:31,440
No big deal.

795
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:34,750
This wallet

796
00:25:34,750 --> 00:25:35,350
is not bad.

797
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:36,960
It has a lot of money.

798
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:37,920
Cao Liu!

799
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:40,920
That's my wallet!

800
00:25:44,830 --> 00:25:45,830
Get out of the way!

801
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:48,770
Sis Bai, wait for me!

802
00:26:04,030 --> 00:26:05,110
You bastard!

803
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:07,350
What are you doing? What are you doing?

804
00:26:07,350 --> 00:26:07,960
Bastard!

805
00:26:07,980 --> 00:26:09,790
You son of a bitch,
give me back my wallet!

806
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:11,990
What are you talking about?
Shoo, shoo.

807
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:13,880
Ke Yixiong!

808
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:15,720
Boss! Boss! Boss!

809
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,160
Keep going.

810
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:25,200
Xiong.

811
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:31,650
I'm telling you,

812
00:26:31,790 --> 00:26:33,250
this better be important.

813
00:26:33,550 --> 00:26:35,080
Or else this round is on you.

814
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:36,070
Boss.

815
00:26:36,850 --> 00:26:37,500
Fei stole

816
00:26:37,520 --> 00:26:38,640
a wallet
from one of Bai Zhenzhu's friends.

817
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:40,100
They chased him down here.

818
00:26:46,100 --> 00:26:47,360
That woman is here too?

819
00:26:47,520 --> 00:26:48,690
It seems so.

820
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:49,860
They were together.

821
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:51,790
Ke Yixiong!

822
00:26:52,510 --> 00:26:53,510
You bastard!

823
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:55,200
Hurry up!

824
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:56,900
Give the wallet back to me!

825
00:26:57,110 --> 00:26:58,440
Give me back the wallet!

826
00:27:03,350 --> 00:27:03,960
Ms. Bai.

827
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,960
You brought a lackey with you today?

828
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:07,880
Shut up.

829
00:27:08,690 --> 00:27:10,020
Give me back the wallet.

830
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:12,640
My brother

831
00:27:13,010 --> 00:27:14,670
picked up your wallet for you.

832
00:27:14,690 --> 00:27:16,790
You're not going to even say "thank you?"

833
00:27:16,790 --> 00:27:18,170
He stole it.

834
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:19,640
Who said you could speak?

835
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:28,790
Ms. Bai,

836
00:27:29,480 --> 00:27:31,160
you used to be just

837
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:33,030
a fruit seller at the train station.

838
00:27:33,030 --> 00:27:34,890
You went to Shengcheng 4 years ago

839
00:27:35,030 --> 00:27:36,490
and started to make it big.

840
00:27:37,100 --> 00:27:38,960
Someone who just knows martial arts,

841
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:39,640
how could you have

842
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:40,830
any business sense?

843
00:27:43,310 --> 00:27:44,270
If you ask me,

844
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:46,720
it was this friend

845
00:27:47,310 --> 00:27:49,640
who introduced you to Shengcheng, right?

846
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:53,140
What are you trying to say?

847
00:27:54,400 --> 00:27:56,160
Nothing much.

848
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:59,000
I'm just quite interested

849
00:27:59,550 --> 00:28:00,510
in this friend.

850
00:28:01,270 --> 00:28:03,200
We should all make money together.

851
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:06,070
Ms. Bai, would you do me the honor

852
00:28:06,550 --> 00:28:08,000
of introducing me

853
00:28:08,590 --> 00:28:09,510
to this friend?

854
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:21,250
Who do you think you are?

855
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:24,030
She runs a legitimate business.

856
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:31,480
Ms. Bai, you've made a lot of money,

857
00:28:31,510 --> 00:28:33,370
but your words are still so harsh.

858
00:28:36,030 --> 00:28:37,030
However,

859
00:28:38,750 --> 00:28:40,000
you are generous.

860
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:42,510
Just pass on a message for me.

861
00:28:48,680 --> 00:28:50,000
Come by often!

862
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,160
Him?

863
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:57,310
A hero?

864
00:28:57,720 --> 00:28:58,920
More like a disgrace.

865
00:28:58,960 --> 00:29:00,270
He's just a local thug.

866
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:02,790
He's basically the boss

867
00:29:02,790 --> 00:29:04,400
of the thugs around the train station.

868
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:05,550
He acts all tough,

869
00:29:06,110 --> 00:29:07,570
but he's actually a loser!

870
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:10,310
Everyone else has legitimate businesses,

871
00:29:10,310 --> 00:29:11,910
but he's still a petty thief.

872
00:29:12,070 --> 00:29:14,310
And he wants to get to know Xiaolan?

873
00:29:14,510 --> 00:29:15,590
Dream on!

874
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:16,680
Exactly!

875
00:29:17,510 --> 00:29:19,000
The bus to Shengcheng

876
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,030
runs every 3 hours.

877
00:29:20,030 --> 00:29:21,030
We have some time.

878
00:29:21,070 --> 00:29:23,600
Let me take you
to try some local specialties.

879
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:25,590
Coming through. Make way.

880
00:29:25,590 --> 00:29:26,030
Watch out.

881
00:29:26,030 --> 00:29:26,440
We're here.

882
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:27,100
Take a look.

883
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:32,030
Sis Bai,

884
00:29:32,030 --> 00:29:33,200
the variety of breakfast

885
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:33,930
you have here

886
00:29:34,130 --> 00:29:35,080
is q-quite the spread.

887
00:29:35,080 --> 00:29:36,350
That's not even all of it.

888
00:29:36,350 --> 00:29:37,660
There are tons of options.

889
00:29:37,660 --> 00:29:39,680
Seafood porridge,
pork and preserved egg porridge,

890
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:40,680
beef porridge with egg...

891
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:41,740
All kinds. Come on.

892
00:29:42,550 --> 00:29:42,920
Sis Bai,

893
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:44,420
you're rattling off the menu like a pro.

894
00:29:44,420 --> 00:29:45,820
You're making me hungry.

895
00:29:46,390 --> 00:29:47,650
Let me have some water.

896
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,750
This isn't for drinking.

897
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:50,690
Give it to me.

898
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:56,350
There are many migrant workers

899
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:57,480
here in Yuesheng now.

900
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:58,000
Doing this

901
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,440
is more hygienic.

902
00:30:00,270 --> 00:30:00,720
Here.

903
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:02,450
Hello. What would you like?

904
00:30:02,600 --> 00:30:03,860
One seafood porridge,

905
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:06,000
chicken feet,

906
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:08,420
and shrimp dumplings.

907
00:30:08,590 --> 00:30:09,640
Looks delicious.

908
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:09,960
Okay.

909
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:11,620
Are you a college student too?

910
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:12,510
Me? No way.

911
00:30:12,510 --> 00:30:14,480
You can't just get into college.

912
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:15,640
I graduated
from a technical middle school.

913
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:17,240
I've been working for years.

914
00:30:17,860 --> 00:30:19,210
Since you're out here traveling,

915
00:30:19,210 --> 00:30:20,340
what about your job?

916
00:30:20,590 --> 00:30:22,310
My job has no future.

917
00:30:22,550 --> 00:30:23,860
It's not as good
as being self-employed like you.

918
00:30:23,860 --> 00:30:24,860
Xiaolan told me

919
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:26,680
you have a stall in Shengcheng

920
00:30:26,830 --> 00:30:28,630
and that your business is great.

921
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:30,600
It's thanks to meeting Xiaolan back then.

922
00:30:30,600 --> 00:30:31,790
She told me to take Longcheng's

923
00:30:31,790 --> 00:30:32,650
cheap trousers

924
00:30:32,860 --> 00:30:35,660
to resell them
at Shengcheng construction sites.

925
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,880
I got

926
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,020
the Border Permit.

927
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,510
I've been to Shengcheng a few times.

928
00:30:39,510 --> 00:30:41,070
But it's all construction sites

929
00:30:41,070 --> 00:30:42,310
still building things up.

930
00:30:42,310 --> 00:30:43,570
What business can I do?

931
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:49,070
This.

932
00:30:50,110 --> 00:30:52,160
I'm not cut out for the clothing business.

933
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:54,220
Maybe I should learn pig butchering.

934
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:56,790
Shengcheng Special Zone
is full of construction sites.

935
00:30:56,790 --> 00:30:57,350
That means

936
00:30:57,350 --> 00:30:58,920
there are construction workers everywhere.

937
00:30:58,920 --> 00:30:59,720
Where there are people,

938
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:00,720
there's a market.

939
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:02,790
Shangdu is an established city, after all.

940
00:31:02,790 --> 00:31:04,510
I stock mid-to-high-end goods there.

941
00:31:04,510 --> 00:31:05,920
In Shengcheng, we need to do the opposite.

942
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:06,880
We need to focus on high volume,

943
00:31:06,880 --> 00:31:08,160
good quality, and low prices.

944
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:09,490
These cheap dress pants

945
00:31:09,590 --> 00:31:10,590
would be perfect.

946
00:31:11,720 --> 00:31:14,160
Will... Will this really work?

947
00:31:14,800 --> 00:31:16,520
Dress pants, 70 a dozen!

948
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:18,070
The more you buy, the cheaper I can go!

949
00:31:18,070 --> 00:31:19,270
Come take a look!

950
00:31:19,750 --> 00:31:20,130
Take a look

951
00:31:20,130 --> 00:31:20,680
at this fabric.

952
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:22,640
How much off if I buy in bulk?

953
00:31:23,550 --> 00:31:24,440
If you buy 100,

954
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:26,000
I'll give you 50% off.

955
00:31:27,590 --> 00:31:28,270
50% off?

956
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:29,310
Trust me.

957
00:31:29,550 --> 00:31:31,150
I'll put up half the capital.

958
00:31:33,510 --> 00:31:34,000
Boss!

959
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:35,030
I'll take 100!

960
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:35,840
Of course!

961
00:31:37,350 --> 00:31:38,790
It's thanks to Xiaolan's advice;

962
00:31:38,790 --> 00:31:40,480
otherwise, the person you see now

963
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:42,340
would just be Sis Bai the butcher.

964
00:31:52,070 --> 00:31:52,650
Sis Bai,

965
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:53,830
Shengcheng is pretty close

966
00:31:53,830 --> 00:31:55,110
to Longcheng,

967
00:31:55,130 --> 00:31:56,660
but it's really different.

968
00:31:56,890 --> 00:31:57,520
Yeah.

969
00:31:57,550 --> 00:32:00,200
Longcheng developed
earlier than Shengcheng.

970
00:32:00,200 --> 00:32:02,460
But Shengcheng has more room for growth.

971
00:32:02,560 --> 00:32:04,160
That's what Xiaolan told me.

972
00:32:04,830 --> 00:32:05,790
Even though she's only

973
00:32:05,790 --> 00:32:07,200
been here a few times for stock,

974
00:32:07,200 --> 00:32:08,000
she seems to know this place

975
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:08,930
better than I do.

976
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:11,680
Is Xiaolan really moving to Shengcheng?

977
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:13,540
I haven't heard Cheng mention it.

978
00:32:13,590 --> 00:32:15,510
I thought
she was just visiting for a few days.

979
00:32:15,510 --> 00:32:17,440
Maybe she hasn't decided yet.

980
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:19,860
By the way,

981
00:32:19,860 --> 00:32:20,320
Sis Bai,

982
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:22,350
y-you always talk about how amazing

983
00:32:22,350 --> 00:32:23,550
the Renmin Bridge is.

984
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:24,270
Where is it?

985
00:32:24,270 --> 00:32:25,130
What's it like?

986
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:25,750
Look!

987
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,440
Once we cross this bridge,

988
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:28,310
you'll see it.

989
00:32:28,470 --> 00:32:30,810
[Welcome to
Renmin Bridge Smallware Market]

990
00:32:28,760 --> 00:32:33,090
♪ Along the long road ahead,
how much beauty awaits ♪

991
00:32:33,120 --> 00:32:36,710
♪ I'll take time to appreciate it all ♪

992
00:32:37,570 --> 00:32:41,470
♪ I'll take time to appreciate it all ♪

993
00:32:42,040 --> 00:32:45,310
♪ My heart feels so confused ♪

994
00:32:45,900 --> 00:32:49,770
♪ Silently, I watch the clouds
drift in the sky ♪

995
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:54,880
♪ Just like you and I,
our ambitions reach far and wide ♪

996
00:32:54,910 --> 00:32:58,870
♪ I hope to wander joyfully with you ♪

997
00:32:57,270 --> 00:32:59,000
Don't miss out!

998
00:32:59,350 --> 00:33:00,440
These are imported goods!

999
00:32:59,530 --> 00:33:04,090
♪ Hand in hand, exploring strange lands ♪

1000
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:02,110
Look how stretchy they are!

1001
00:33:02,240 --> 00:33:03,570
They're great. Buy one!

1002
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:05,270
This is the latest style from Gangdao!

1003
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:08,720
♪ The road ahead is full of storms ♪

1004
00:33:05,270 --> 00:33:06,440
Bell-bottoms!

1005
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:07,830
Do you want any cassettes?

1006
00:33:07,830 --> 00:33:09,250
We have Jacky Cheung and Andy Lau!

1007
00:33:09,250 --> 00:33:12,630
♪ I'll get by them one by one ♪

1008
00:33:09,550 --> 00:33:11,410
Hey pretty lady, come take a look.

1009
00:33:11,590 --> 00:33:12,720
You're so pretty,

1010
00:33:12,750 --> 00:33:13,620
and your voice is so sweet.

1011
00:33:13,620 --> 00:33:17,630
♪ We'll guard each other
on the road ahead ♪

1012
00:33:13,920 --> 00:33:14,920
We can do 180 yuan.

1013
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:15,480
How much?

1014
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:16,310
That's too expensive.

1015
00:33:16,310 --> 00:33:17,270
That's half a month's wages!

1016
00:33:17,270 --> 00:33:18,110
Too expensive.

1017
00:33:18,110 --> 00:33:19,160
That year, when Zhenzhu and I

1018
00:33:18,650 --> 00:33:21,420
♪ Don't be afraid of the long path ♪

1019
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:20,480
first came to Renmin Bridge,

1020
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:22,050
they only sold cheap goods around here.

1021
00:33:22,050 --> 00:33:25,760
♪ With you,
there won't be despair on this path ♪

1022
00:33:22,110 --> 00:33:23,160
Later, as more and more people

1023
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:23,920
came here to shop,

1024
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:24,790
these trendy clothes

1025
00:33:24,790 --> 00:33:26,250
started selling well too.

1026
00:33:26,590 --> 00:33:27,880
I finally found you!

1027
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:29,000
Is the luggage dropped off?

1028
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:29,510
Yes.

1029
00:33:29,550 --> 00:33:31,280
They are all in the guesthouse.

1030
00:33:31,590 --> 00:33:33,480
It's my first time here too.

1031
00:33:33,750 --> 00:33:34,950
It's quite bustling.

1032
00:33:35,140 --> 00:33:35,670
Mrs. Liu.

1033
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:36,680
Look at these.

1034
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:37,880
They must be imports.

1035
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:40,030
Xiaolan!

1036
00:33:40,790 --> 00:33:41,510
Coming!

1037
00:33:41,590 --> 00:33:42,350
Let's go, Mom.

1038
00:33:42,350 --> 00:33:42,750
Yong.

1039
00:33:47,010 --> 00:33:48,200
This is my stall right here.

1040
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:48,800
Come look.

1041
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:49,680
You're back!

1042
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:50,140
Senior!

1043
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:51,160
I'll be going then.

1044
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,400
Thanks, Senior.

1045
00:33:52,400 --> 00:33:53,270
Thank you.

1046
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:54,070
Have a good time here

1047
00:33:54,070 --> 00:33:54,590
with your friends.

1048
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:55,200
We will.

1049
00:33:55,590 --> 00:33:56,120
Bye-bye.

1050
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:57,530
Mrs. Liu,

1051
00:33:57,590 --> 00:33:58,270
have some

1052
00:33:58,650 --> 00:33:59,110
herbal tea.

1053
00:33:59,110 --> 00:33:59,570
Thanks.

1054
00:33:59,590 --> 00:34:00,510
I can't handle this.

1055
00:34:00,510 --> 00:34:01,880
It's all over the streets in Longcheng.

1056
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:03,310
I just can't get used to it.

1057
00:34:03,310 --> 00:34:04,840
I still prefer plain water.

1058
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:05,680
Mom, try it.

1059
00:34:05,830 --> 00:34:07,000
When I stock up in Longcheng,

1060
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:07,790
I drink it often.

1061
00:34:07,790 --> 00:34:08,400
Let me try.

1062
00:34:12,070 --> 00:34:13,929
It tastes like Chinese medicine.

1063
00:34:14,070 --> 00:34:15,190
It's okay. I can get it down.

1064
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:16,510
Yeah. The climate here

1065
00:34:16,510 --> 00:34:17,440
is hot and humid.

1066
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:20,040
Drinking this
relieves the dampness and heat.

1067
00:34:20,150 --> 00:34:20,679
Zhenzhu,

1068
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:22,070
I see that

1069
00:34:22,070 --> 00:34:24,130
you're selling quite varied things.

1070
00:34:24,409 --> 00:34:25,199
Yeah.

1071
00:34:25,230 --> 00:34:27,190
At first, I only sold clothes.

1072
00:34:27,400 --> 00:34:28,110
Then I realized

1073
00:34:28,110 --> 00:34:30,150
there were
too many people selling clothes.

1074
00:34:30,150 --> 00:34:31,630
So I just followed the trend.

1075
00:34:31,630 --> 00:34:33,159
I sell whatever is popular.

1076
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:34,480
Is it profitable?

1077
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:36,630
I did make money.

1078
00:34:37,630 --> 00:34:38,550
In Shengcheng,

1079
00:34:38,840 --> 00:34:39,920
as long as you're not lazy

1080
00:34:39,920 --> 00:34:40,760
and willing to learn,

1081
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:41,760
you won't starve.

1082
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:44,360
This place is interesting.

1083
00:34:44,360 --> 00:34:45,230
Your stall is so big.

1084
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:47,030
Why don't you get a proper shop?

1085
00:34:48,590 --> 00:34:49,320
Don't get me started.

1086
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,730
I wanted to get a shop too.

1087
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:51,920
But right now,

1088
00:34:52,230 --> 00:34:54,440
though there are
"For Sale" signs on the shops,

1089
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:55,670
when you actually call,

1090
00:34:55,670 --> 00:34:56,710
no one answers.

1091
00:34:57,340 --> 00:34:58,300
After a while,

1092
00:34:58,330 --> 00:34:59,790
a new tenant would move in.

1093
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:01,440
It's all done internally.

1094
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:02,510
Zhenzhu,

1095
00:35:02,710 --> 00:35:04,030
you really need a shop.

1096
00:35:04,200 --> 00:35:05,840
The scale will be different with a shop.

1097
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:07,900
You can't be a street vendor forever.

1098
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:09,110
I understand that.

1099
00:35:09,590 --> 00:35:11,120
I'll figure something out.

1100
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:13,240
It's not that
I don't want to treat you to a big meal.

1101
00:35:13,240 --> 00:35:14,360
It's just that at Renmin Bridge,

1102
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:15,190
you must try

1103
00:35:15,190 --> 00:35:16,390
our local specialty—

1104
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,210
boxed meals!

1105
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:17,710
Come!

1106
00:35:18,070 --> 00:35:19,670
Freshly made and piping hot!

1107
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:20,550
There's char siu.

1108
00:35:20,550 --> 00:35:21,880
Here, come on.

1109
00:35:36,760 --> 00:35:38,090
What do you want to have?

1110
00:35:45,480 --> 00:35:46,410
You like it here?

1111
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:49,590
It's something I'm looking forward to.

1112
00:35:49,590 --> 00:35:51,480
When I chose architecture,

1113
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:54,010
this was the future I envisioned.

1114
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:56,110
Noisy construction sites,

1115
00:35:56,110 --> 00:35:56,800
sweat,

1116
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:57,590
and dust.

1117
00:35:58,110 --> 00:35:59,440
I've only seen this on TV

1118
00:35:59,440 --> 00:35:59,920
before.

1119
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:01,590
I never thought one day,

1120
00:36:01,590 --> 00:36:02,280
I could finally

1121
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:03,480
stop being a bystander

1122
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:05,670
and become someone participating in it.

1123
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:06,710
I hope one day

1124
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:08,760
I can also design and build

1125
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:09,920
a house of my own.

1126
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:11,880
If you want to design houses,

1127
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:13,070
you'd have to go to

1128
00:36:13,070 --> 00:36:14,400
a design institute
after graduating, right?

1129
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:16,760
Design institutes are so rigid.

1130
00:36:17,030 --> 00:36:17,840
Who knows how long it'll take

1131
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:18,970
to achieve my dream.

1132
00:36:19,230 --> 00:36:21,110
Shengcheng is developing fast.

1133
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:22,640
I need to speed up too.

1134
00:36:23,560 --> 00:36:24,280
Sir,

1135
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:25,550
one char siu rice.

1136
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:26,770
Two. Make it two.

1137
00:36:26,850 --> 00:36:28,230
Two? Okay, two char siu rice.

1138
00:36:28,230 --> 00:36:29,760
Sir, I'm paying!

1139
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,110
Okay, sure!

1140
00:36:33,070 --> 00:36:33,840
Try it, quick.

1141
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:34,150
Okay.

1142
00:36:34,150 --> 00:36:35,590
Our char siu is delicious.

1143
00:36:35,590 --> 00:36:36,400
Hurry up!

1144
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:37,550
Thank you, Mrs. Liu.

1145
00:36:37,550 --> 00:36:38,320
Try it.

1146
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,280
It tastes different

1147
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:40,140
from back home.

1148
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:41,320
Try it.

1149
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:43,670
It's good.

1150
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:44,150
It is.

1151
00:36:44,710 --> 00:36:45,480
What are your plans

1152
00:36:45,480 --> 00:36:46,590
after we eat?

1153
00:36:47,370 --> 00:36:47,920
Sis Bai,

1154
00:36:48,190 --> 00:36:50,390
I want to try setting up a stall with you.

1155
00:36:50,550 --> 00:36:51,710
Are you serious?

1156
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:54,550
Just don't complain that it's hard work.

1157
00:36:54,550 --> 00:36:55,020
Xiaolan,

1158
00:36:55,020 --> 00:36:55,710
I have to go back

1159
00:36:55,710 --> 00:36:56,880
to the construction site later.

1160
00:36:56,880 --> 00:36:58,150
You show Mom around.

1161
00:37:03,030 --> 00:37:04,510
It's so beautiful!

1162
00:37:07,030 --> 00:37:08,320
Be careful, Mom!

1163
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,510
So beautiful.

1164
00:37:16,030 --> 00:37:16,760
Come up here.

1165
00:37:21,920 --> 00:37:23,280
I never thought in this life

1166
00:37:23,280 --> 00:37:24,880
I'd see such a beautiful sea.

1167
00:37:25,480 --> 00:37:26,480
Why not?

1168
00:37:26,800 --> 00:37:27,600
In the future,

1169
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:29,440
I'll take you to more places

1170
00:37:29,550 --> 00:37:30,880
to see the bigger world.

1171
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:32,750
Mom,

1172
00:37:33,150 --> 00:37:34,110
do you like it here?

1173
00:37:34,110 --> 00:37:35,440
If you like it, I like it.

1174
00:37:36,240 --> 00:37:37,030
Wherever you go,

1175
00:37:37,030 --> 00:37:38,830
I'll follow and take care of you.

1176
00:37:38,920 --> 00:37:40,000
Comrade Liu Fen,

1177
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:41,880
you're not my accessory.

1178
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:43,440
I want you to really like it.

1179
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:45,030
I really do.

1180
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:46,810
Okay!

1181
00:37:47,250 --> 00:37:48,500
After I graduate,

1182
00:37:48,670 --> 00:37:49,960
we'll move here to Shengcheng.

1183
00:37:49,960 --> 00:37:51,400
When we live here then,

1184
00:37:51,730 --> 00:37:53,060
we can be just like this,

1185
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:55,150
enjoying the breeze and seafood.

1186
00:37:55,590 --> 00:37:56,250
How's that?

1187
00:38:02,790 --> 00:38:03,670
Typhoon!

1188
00:38:14,190 --> 00:38:15,510
We really need a shop.

1189
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:16,320
Otherwise, a simple rain

1190
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:18,120
can make life miserable for you.

1191
00:38:18,150 --> 00:38:18,480
Yeah.

1192
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:20,010
It won't stop anytime soon.

1193
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:22,150
Wait.

1194
00:38:22,510 --> 00:38:24,030
Cheng didn't bring umbrellas.

1195
00:38:24,030 --> 00:38:24,760
The rain is so heavy.

1196
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:26,020
How will they get back?

1197
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:30,590
How did this rain

1198
00:38:30,590 --> 00:38:31,920
just start pouring out of nowhere?

1199
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:33,840
With rain this heavy,
there won't be any cars.

1200
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:36,570
Let's wait for the rain
to let up a bit before we go.

1201
00:38:37,550 --> 00:38:38,190
If the rain

1202
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:39,190
doesn't stop before dark,

1203
00:38:39,190 --> 00:38:40,400
I'll go over there to make a call.

1204
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:40,760
Okay.

1205
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:43,670
Here.

1206
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:44,260
Hold on.

1207
00:38:45,510 --> 00:38:46,000
Slowly.

1208
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:47,320
Slowly.

1209
00:38:48,360 --> 00:38:49,890
Xiaolan, Zhou Cheng, look.

1210
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:54,030
Let's go take a look.

1211
00:38:54,030 --> 00:38:54,590
Let's go.

1212
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:59,290
What's wrong? Are you okay?

1213
00:38:59,400 --> 00:38:59,930
Comrade,

1214
00:39:00,110 --> 00:39:01,040
do you need help?

1215
00:39:01,110 --> 00:39:02,630
My boss's stomach is acting up.

1216
00:39:02,630 --> 00:39:04,150
I want to take him to the clinic,

1217
00:39:04,150 --> 00:39:05,410
but the car broke down.

1218
00:39:05,710 --> 00:39:06,760
Here, give it to me.

1219
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:08,090
Help him up. Help him up.

1220
00:39:08,630 --> 00:39:09,030
Here.

1221
00:39:09,510 --> 00:39:10,510
There's one more umbrella.

1222
00:39:10,510 --> 00:39:11,190
Be careful!

1223
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:25,520
It's okay.

1224
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:27,920
Are you all right?

1225
00:39:28,110 --> 00:39:29,590
I'm sorry. Sorry. So sorry.

1226
00:39:29,590 --> 00:39:30,760
It's fine. It's fine.

1227
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:31,110
Slow down.

1228
00:39:31,110 --> 00:39:31,550
Let me do it.

1229
00:39:31,550 --> 00:39:32,750
Thank you. Thank you.

1230
00:39:34,070 --> 00:39:35,400
Wipe yourself off more.

1231
00:39:35,440 --> 00:39:36,000
I'm fine now.

1232
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:36,600
Look how wet your hair is.

1233
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:37,190
Let me dry it for you.

1234
00:39:37,190 --> 00:39:38,720
I'm fine. I'm okay. No need.

1235
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:40,550
Come here.

1236
00:39:40,550 --> 00:39:41,760
For you to dry your clothes.

1237
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:42,480
Don't let yourselves collapse

1238
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:43,590
before the patient even recovers.

1239
00:39:43,590 --> 00:39:44,550
Thank you, Doctor.

1240
00:39:44,550 --> 00:39:45,880
He has acute gastritis.

1241
00:39:46,030 --> 00:39:47,550
It's best not to take medicine
on an empty stomach.

1242
00:39:47,550 --> 00:39:48,630
This is a small clinic.

1243
00:39:48,630 --> 00:39:50,000
We don't have a cafeteria.

1244
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:51,030
We still need to find a way

1245
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:52,280
to get him something bland to eat.

1246
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:52,610
Okay.

1247
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:56,510
Please.

1248
00:39:56,510 --> 00:39:57,570
Okay. Give it to me.

1249
00:39:57,980 --> 00:39:59,560
Mrs. Liu, I'll go out

1250
00:39:59,590 --> 00:40:00,110
to see if there is

1251
00:40:00,110 --> 00:40:00,890
anything to cook porridge in.

1252
00:40:00,890 --> 00:40:02,090
Okay, okay. Go ahead.

1253
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:45,280
Wang.

1254
00:40:48,510 --> 00:40:49,230
Mr. Tang.

1255
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:50,320
You're awake.

1256
00:40:53,140 --> 00:40:54,710
Wang went to borrow a phone.

1257
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:57,660
I'll go get the doctor.

1258
00:41:16,070 --> 00:41:16,870
You're awake.

1259
00:41:17,610 --> 00:41:18,470
How do you feel?

1260
00:41:19,030 --> 00:41:19,830
I'm all right.

1261
00:41:21,990 --> 00:41:23,250
How is it? Does it hurt?

1262
00:41:23,510 --> 00:41:24,910
It doesn't hurt anymore.

1263
00:41:25,030 --> 00:41:25,890
How about here?

1264
00:41:27,230 --> 00:41:27,630
Nope.

1265
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:30,080
Being able to eat is a good thing.

1266
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:31,800
But you should treat

1267
00:41:32,070 --> 00:41:34,310
your chronic stomach problem properly
when you have time.

1268
00:41:34,310 --> 00:41:36,400
If you're fine, you can be discharged.

1269
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,000
Remember to eat on time back home.

1270
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,000
Stick to a light diet.

1271
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:39,330
Okay.

1272
00:41:39,590 --> 00:41:40,510
Okay, thank you.

1273
00:41:40,510 --> 00:41:41,150
Thank you, Doctor.

1274
00:41:41,150 --> 00:41:42,080
You're welcome.

1275
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:45,180
Thank you, too.

1276
00:41:45,510 --> 00:41:46,510
Don't mention it.

1277
00:41:49,710 --> 00:41:51,040
My name is Tang Hong'en.

1278
00:41:51,420 --> 00:41:52,420
My name is Liu Fen.

1279
00:41:57,400 --> 00:41:58,590
Can you get me another bowl?

1280
00:41:58,590 --> 00:41:59,840
Sure, no problem.

1281
00:42:14,550 --> 00:42:15,440
It's a bit hot.

1282
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:16,880
Well...

1283
00:42:19,800 --> 00:42:20,280
Well...

1284
00:42:20,920 --> 00:42:21,580
Let me do it.

1285
00:42:23,670 --> 00:42:24,030
Here.

1286
00:42:24,760 --> 00:42:26,070
You're still on an IV drip.

1287
00:42:26,070 --> 00:42:26,400
Here.

1288
00:42:33,630 --> 00:42:34,000
Here.

1289
00:42:45,670 --> 00:42:46,670
I'll do it myself.

1290
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:48,840
Thanks.

1291
00:42:49,440 --> 00:42:49,840
Okay.

1292
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:53,480
Thank you.

1293
00:43:01,190 --> 00:43:02,250
Careful, it's hot.

1294
00:43:10,550 --> 00:43:11,510
May I ask,

1295
00:43:12,590 --> 00:43:13,650
where are you from?

1296
00:43:14,320 --> 00:43:15,880
We are from Anqing, Yunan.

1297
00:43:16,960 --> 00:43:18,020
You are from Yunan?

1298
00:43:20,630 --> 00:43:22,540
I'm quite familiar with that place.

1299
00:43:22,540 --> 00:43:23,990
I used to work there.

1300
00:43:24,320 --> 00:43:25,320
What a coincidence!
